OL,3,CAround 6% of UK adults diagnosed with
OL,4,Cfood allergies, study reveals
OL,6,FNadim Ednan-Laperouse, whose daughter
OL,7,FNatasha died in 2016 after suffering a
OL,8,Fsevere allergic reaction to sesame
OL,9,Fbaked into a Pret baguette, and who is
OL,10,Fnow co-founder of The Natasha Allergy
OL,11,FResearch Foundation, said: "This is a
OL,12,Fhugely significant study which
OL,13,Fconfirms our view that there is a food
OL,14,Fallergy epidemic in this country.
