OL,3,CAround 6% of UK adults diagnosed with
OL,4,Cfood allergies, study reveals
OL,6,F"With the true number of people with
OL,7,Ffood allergies in this country now
OL,8,Frunning into millions, it is
OL,9,Fimperative that we provide joined up
OL,10,FNHS services and proper support for
OL,11,Feveryone with food allergies. We would
OL,12,Furge the Government to appoint an
OL,13,Fallergy tsar to fulfil this unmet
OL,14,Fneed."
