OL,3,CAround 6% of UK adults diagnosed with
OL,4,Cfood allergies, study reveals
OL,6,FThe FSA's chief scientific adviser,
OL,7,FProfessor Robin May, said: "The PAFA
OL,8,Freport is significant in helping us
OL,9,Fidentify how food allergies evolve
OL,10,Fbetween childhood and adulthood, as
OL,11,Fwell as providing vital insights into
OL,12,Flinks between certain types of foods
OL,13,Fand the persistence of allergies into
OL,14,Fadulthood.
